---
title: Southern Style Chicken and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Sometimes you need to get inventive to get the nippers to try something new. Kids these days are wising up to the old ‘hide-the-veg-in-the-pastasauce’ trick, so we’ve been trying out a few sneaky ways to respin some
decadent favourites. Tonight, we’re taking southern fried chicken and giving it a total makeover.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southern-style-chicken-wk43-d444d72e.jpg
